        "gg3LCZKwLyt_text": "<p><strong>Swedish study (1987): </strong>91% of sciatica is disc dehydration</p>",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Grounded in Real Science. Trusted by Professionals.",
        "gg8AUpoc7KP_text": "<p>Boosted confidence walking, bending, and standing</p>",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "The Entire Country Is Raving About the SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro",
        "ggEp2TI9fEZ_text": "<p><strong>Hides et al. (1994): </strong>EMS restores muscle function in chronic pain patients</p>",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "The Entire Country Is Raving About the SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro",
        "ggKxNI6U9MA_text": "<p><strong>NASA study (2001): </strong>Red light accelerates tissue healing by 40%</p>",
        "ggOLny2Lf9H_text": "<p>Better sleep—waking up rested instead of stiff</p>",
        "ggSvIZrM2QP_text": "<p>The energy to do things you’ve been avoiding for years</p>",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro was engineered in collaboration with orthopedic surgeons and licensed physical therapists who’ve spent decades treating chronic back pain and sciatica.</p>",
        "ggUraYE6NrG_text": "<p><strong>Saal &amp; Saal (1989):</strong> Non-surgical decompression = 86% success rate</p>",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/cd7d2dc070d54eaaad2fcc53e7a99f7b.mp4",
