    "gp_section_595501561191727714": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "82b501aa0618316daf77bcfbd153feab30da9a35f918962cfb64a0a91cf4538a_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg7gfYbpkbD_text": "<p>EMS strengthens support muscles</p>",
        "gg9sfrUDNiv_text": "Why This Works When Everything Else Failed",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>Pills mask pain. Stretching can’t create enough decompression. Massage alone doesn’t fix structural degradation. And chiropractors are temporary without disc healing.</p>",
        "ggLpXZltW4C_text": "<p>It’s not symptom management. It’s elimination of the source of your pain.</p>",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "Why This Works When Everything Else Failed",
        "ggNxAHEd9SQ_text": "<p><strong>SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro</strong> attacks the <strong>ROOT CAUSE:</strong></p>",
        "ggP5xbHg6z-_text": "<p>Red light reduces inflammation</p>",
        "ggP9YY587P1_text": "<p>Forces fluid back into discs using deep heat</p>",
        "gg_-MJSPsBq_text": "<p>Creates 3–7mm vertebral separation (clinical decompression threshold)</p>",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/b921dd29b38246bd880ed00450f0d2ad.mp4",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/Screenshot_14.webp",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggd9w5iVAlN_text": "<p>Your discs didn’t dehydrate overnight. They won’t fully rehydrate overnight. But healing starts immediately.</p>",
        "ggiF75sp5pb_text": "<p>Massage releases tension, improves circulation</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-595501561191727714"
    },
    "gp_section_595501561191793250": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "086b969ee231689d354e93c73d3cc42b21c78fc4f97fd4a28f216efab4a39371_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0045cZav__text": "<p>Your vertebrae crush closer together. The space for your nerves shrinks. And your sciatic nerve? It gets squeezed like a garden hose under a truck tire.</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>It’s not about your muscles. It’s not about your posture. It’s not even about inflammation.</p>",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>Imagine Waking Up Tomorrow Without That First Jolt of Pain</strong></span>",
        "ggN5O792d2I_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/240ec8e538074993b7ead7f902e0f92c.mp4",
        "ggN5O792d2I_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/Screenshot_11.webp",
        "ggN5O792d2I_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN5O792d2I_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>It’s about your spinal discs – the shock absorbers between your vertebrae – slowly dying from dehydration.</p>",
        "ggRTR9XYKM9_text": "<p>Your discs are 80% water. When you’re young, they’re plump, juicy, full of fluid. They keep your vertebrae separated and your nerves happy.</p>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "Your Spine Is Literally Suffocating – And Pills Won’t Save It",
        "ggWaLe4w3DQ_text": "<p>But after age 30, those discs start losing fluid. Getting thinner. Flatter. Like sponges left in the sun.</p>",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Here’s what nobody tells you about chronic back pain and sciatica:</p>",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "Your Spine Is Literally Suffocating – And Pills Won’t Save It"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-595501561191793250"
    },
    "gp_section_595501561191858786": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "47d78a1933c822e26827b0695c433184c6937e6e45b2d040ce5ee3fc9a762f06_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1rlZNSakA_text": "<p>Simply get yourself a <strong>SmoothSpine™ - Multi Therapy Pro</strong> today, use it for 90 days, and then make your decision based on the results. <strong>If you are not absolutely thrilled with the relief, we will issue you an immediate refund.</strong></p>",
        "ggCn6xOSitZ_text": "<p>That’s why we are offering a <strong>90-day “Results or Refund” guarantee.</strong></p>",
        "ggDerpXpkv1_text": "Try It For 90 Days, 100% Risk-Free",
        "ggGwm1Shj_V_text": "<p>In other words, you are only paying if it <strong>truly works</strong> and helps you reclaim a pain-free life.</p>",
        "ggNH0yZYdL0_text": "Try It for 90 Days, 100% Risk-Free",
        "ggNmha1SiOD_text": "<p>Here’s the deal: We believe in this product so much that <strong>we don’t want you to spend a dime until you are 100% certain that it works for you.</strong></p>",
        "ggr-cdETAvt_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f56efdea-c394-4196-8c2d-0c85230a19dc.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-595501561191858786"
    },
    "gp_section_595501561191924322": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "66fe241473fbaaccec440dacc506dbafa7cdb3db808535b90cb5974b06ea09bc_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg029TQ7PQT_text": "<p>\"I Thought I Was Too Far Gone.\"</p>",
        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>\"My Doctor Called It 'Medically Impossible'\"</p>",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>\"It Beat My $8,000 in Physical Therapy\"</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>\"Eight months of PT. Three times a week. $8,000 out of pocket. I got maybe 10% better. Then I'd tweak my back and be back to square one. Got the SmoothSpine out of desperation. Within TWO WEEKS, I felt better than I had in eight months of professional therapy. Turns out I didn't need more stretches. I needed decompression, heat, massage, and EMS working together.\"</p>",
        "ggQgcHb_VvV_text": "<p>— Linda McCarthy, 52, Verified Purchase</p>",
        "ggReBUA1njy_text": "<p>— Amanda Peterson, 44, Verified Purchase</p>",
