        "ggVUrtxKQwR_text": "<p>Most users feel relief during their first session. But real transformation comes with consistency – use it 1–2 times daily for at least 2 weeks.</p>",
        "ggW-RofZ-mH_text": "<p>Place it on a firm, flat surface – floor or sturdy bed. Lie down with it positioned against your lower back.</p>",
